Package: rgovspeak
Type: Package
Title: Allows govespeak markdown to be used in rmarkdown documents.
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Mark Kirby [aut, cre]
Description: Allows govespeak markdown to be used in rmarkdown documents.
    Creates a markdown file compatable with Whitehall publisher and provides
    a html preview of the document as if it were published to gov.uk.
